"event"},{"source":"recKkbZvoGokiDHJ1","target":"recN1gyMPKbPPQIMa","label":"event"},{"source":"recKkbZvoGokiDHJ1","target":"recOZxrWd00qyF4Ej","label":"event"}],"verses":[{"id":"recj6a38yTTatJuJP","ref":"Luke.21.1","text":"And he looked up, and saw the rich men casting their gifts into the treasury.","year":33},{"id":"recpt8G1xiaGKf6fZ","ref":"Luke.21.2","text":"And he saw also a certain poor widow casting in thither two mites.","year":33},{"id":"recI1Eay4vJXc0HPa","ref":"Luke.21.3","text":"And he said, Of a truth I say unto you, that this poor widow hath cast in more than they all:","year":33},{"id":"recpQXFjlnWLuFEPW","ref":"Luke.21.4","text":"For all these have of their abundance cast in unto the offerings of God: but she of her penury hath cast in all the living that she had.","year":33},{"id":"recAqEzhJmIo0JP64","ref":"Luke.21.5","text":"And as some spake of the temple, how it was adorned with goodly stones and gifts, he said,","year":33},{"id":"rec5RUmrc8fYImBPN","ref":"Luke.21.6","text":"As for these things which ye behold, the days will come, in the which there shall not be left one stone upon another, that shall not be thrown down.","year":33},{"id":"recWxVngQcmN5ICN4","ref":"Luke.21.7","text":"And they asked him, saying, Master, but when shall these things be? and what sign will there be when these things shall come to pass?","year":33},{"id":"recKxD8l3vAZMVudE","ref":"Luke.21.8","text":"And he said, Take heed that ye be not deceived: for many shall come in my name, saying, I am Christ; and the time draweth near: go ye not therefore after them.","year":33}]}
